cont''d 2. The remaining past due balances will be endeavored to be paid at the earliest, subject to a successful capital raise at either the TIFIN or Magnifi level. Agree on an amendment for the agreed-upon terms, retroactive to September 1st. Magnifi will continue to pay quarterly fees of $87,500 in arrears and on time.Thank you,Rick
